How to play video game ðŸŽ®

1. Start the Game

- Click Start button.

  2.How to play the game
  Player has to use up and down key's also right and left key' to guide the key through the labyrinth
  to the house.

3. Win or Reset
   The game detects wins or loss and displays the result.

_Click Reset to restart the game_.

